examples/pdfdiff/

# Private real-world test papers (past articles): never published in the
# public repo. These live in a SEPARATE PRIVATE repo wired in as a git
# submodule at examples/realworld/ (see PLAN.md "real-world" section).
#
# IMPORTANT: once examples/realworld/ is added as a submodule, REMOVE the
# ignore line below — a submodule path must be tracked (as a gitlink), and
# cannot be both ignored and a submodule. The line is kept for now (before
# the submodule exists) only to prevent accidentally committing the loose
# papers into the public repo.
examples/realworld/
